Dialogue: 10,0:01:30.32,0:01:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,"Oh look, dear. It's snowing."
Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.36,0:01:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}"That's okay. I've drunk so much sake, \NI'm wearing a sa-cape."
Dialogue: 10,0:01:47.34,0:01:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:48.71,0:01:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Who will you be giving Valentine's chocolate to?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.97,0:01:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Valentine's?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.47,0:01:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not long now.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.93,0:01:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,About... another six months?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:56.18,0:01:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Your bar for "not long" is way off!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.14,0:02:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So, who are you going to give chocolate to?
Comment: 9,0:02:03.31,0:02:06.36,Alt,,50,350,28,,{\an7\fs48\shad0}Note: Ebizou, A famous kabuki performer.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.31,0:02:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? Ebi***.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.56,0:02:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebi***.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.36,0:02:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, looks like we're all going for Ebi***.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.11,0:02:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'all are full of bull!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.74,0:02:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kabuki? More like ka-bae-ki, am I right?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.49,0:02:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are such idiots, y'know.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.37,0:02:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Giving away chocolate?
