Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.41,0:02:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(0,200)}Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.41,0:02:21.62,Default,,34,366,0,,{\an4\fad(0,200)}Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.41,0:02:21.62,Default,,348,52,0,,{\an6\fad(0,200)}Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.41,0:02:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.62,0:02:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Delivery for you, Miss Marii!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.04,0:02:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Marii's the type of woman who \Ngets chocolate from other women.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.76,0:02:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a Marii at every all-girls school.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.30,0:02:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I dunno if you'd call them dominant \Nor tomboys or what.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.76,0:02:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}That doesn't account for getting \Nso many gifts, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.06,0:02:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we're making an incorrect assumption.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.93,0:02:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Could Marii secretly be a guy?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.10,0:02:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like everyone's getting suspicious.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.94,0:02:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,D-D-Don't be so ridiculous!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.02,0:02:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look at me! What part of me looks like a boy?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.07,0:02:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Marii doesn't look like a boy at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.86,0:02:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, Kigu!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.70,0:02:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He's obviously taken a lot of care with his disguise.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.24,0:03:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.91,0:03:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We shouldn't have said Marii looks like a boy.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.83,0:03:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait just a moment!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.25,0:03:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I'd rather you thought I was a boy than \Nyou thought I was a boy dressed as a girl!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.00,0:03:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a dude, and I'm not a cross-dresser!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.67,0:03:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Once you realise he's a boy, \Nit all starts to make sense.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.97,0:03:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The way he speaks is so aggressive.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.51,0:03:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just how Tokyoites talk!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.14,0:03:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You jerk!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.35,0:03:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Marii is from Tokushima.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.35,0:03:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Did you don this Tokyoite act \Nto bolster your disguise?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.14,0:03:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't don anything!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.19,0:03:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't we being a little cruel?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.85,0:03:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, Tetora!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.90,0:03:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Even if Marii is a boy, that doesn't mean \NI'm going to treat him any differently.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.78,0:03:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Marii is still Marii. That hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.20,0:03:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, come on.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.49,0:03:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.82,0:03:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry, Marii.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.66,0:03:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's keep being friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.54,0:03:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We're BFFs forever!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.75,0:03:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what you need to apologise for!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.46,0:03:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm neither a boy nor am I cross-dressing!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.96,0:03:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a bloody girl!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.25,0:03:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, they're scared.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.59,0:03:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a girl!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.17,0:03:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys don't {\i1}actually{\i0} doubt me, do you?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.39,0:04:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't doubt you.
