Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.14,0:04:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't doubt you at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.72,0:04:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You lot totally doubt me!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.52,0:04:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't doubt you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.19,0:04:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}If that's all you have to say, \Nyou've left me no choice.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.40,0:04:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll prove once and for all that I'm a girl!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.94,0:04:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.61,0:04:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Undressing like that is pretty masculine.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.19,0:04:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Yeah, a lady would never undress \Nout of the blue like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.32,0:04:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Then what's it gonna take to prove \Nto you that I'm a woman?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.24,0:04:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How about showing us some ladylike behaviour?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.91,0:04:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ladylike behaviour?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.87,0:04:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of behaviour counts as ladylike?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.79,0:04:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... For example...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.75,0:04:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How about sitting like a lady?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.47,0:04:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.64,0:04:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Even {\i1}you{\i0} can sit in a ladylike way!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.18,0:04:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I know I can!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.60,0:04:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There, I did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.89,0:04:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you just admit I'm a girl already?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.32,0:04:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}The inner thigh contains \Na great deal of potential energy.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.53,0:05:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like that was a little much.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.36,0:05:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Maybe sitting like a lady was \Ntoo high for the first hurdle?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.41,0:05:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we start with standing like a lady?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.04,0:05:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Knees together, heels apart.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.54,0:05:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Big toes pointing inward.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.50,0:05:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There! That's it.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.34,0:05:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}This time the energy was transferred \Nto the surrounding area!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.68,0:05:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,O-One more time!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.93,0:05:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta let me try one more time!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.72,0:05:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! It could cause untold damage!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.81,0:05:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! I can do the standing thing, I swear!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.56,0:05:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,At least practice somewhere with open spaces.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.23,0:05:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.02,0:05:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just had a great idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.24,0:05:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to explain:
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.61,0:05:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Marii, who can't stand in a ladylike way, \Nsupplies only the top half,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.12,0:05:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}while the bottom half is provided by \Nsomeone with the ability she lacks.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.04,0:05:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Together, they form one ladylike Marii.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.58,0:05:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's out-of-the-box but completely logical.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.13,0:05:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He's doing it!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.21,0:05:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He really is.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.00,0:05:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Shaddup!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.88,0:05:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You look so ladylike, Marii!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.09,0:06:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it! You really did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.26,0:06:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.43,0:06:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What are y'all celebrating for?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.26,0:06:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't solved the original problem!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.51,0:06:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Which was... what again, exactly?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.43,0:06:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We were wondering how he can prove he's a girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.31,0:06:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.94,0:06:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Forget about the outside. Why don't you \Nshow us how feminine you are on the inside?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.36,0:06:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Like being quick to cry.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.74,0:06:20.78,Default,,0,0,45,,{\frx354}Like being quick to cry.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.78,0:06:20.82,Default,,0,0,61,,{\frx354}Like being quick to cry.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.82,0:06:20.86,Default,,0,0,43,,{\frx326}Like being quick to cry.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.86,0:06:20.90,Default,,0,0,61,,{\frx326}Like being quick to cry.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.90,0:06:20.94,Default,,0,0,37,,{\frx304}Like being quick to cry.
